  "The International Astronomical Union reclassified Pluto as a dwarf planet in 2006 because it hasn't cleared its orbital neighborhood.": "",
  "A dwarf planet differs from a planet because it:": "",
  "Is too small to have gravity": "",
  "Has not cleared its orbital neighborhood of other debris": "",
  "Has no atmosphere": "",
  "Does not orbit the Sun": "",
  "A dwarf planet orbits the Sun and has enough gravity for a round shape, but has not cleared its orbital zone.": "",
